song.title: Kenshiro
song.info:
This is part of a group of modules called from the author "Area 05: Hokuto No Ken".
"Kenshiro: *!* Remake from the 1st Hokuto No Ken! Great reproduction with vocal Session: 1st singer - Francesco Oliverio, 2nd singer - Fabio Barzagli + Rearranged part with guitar solos !"
